To launch the angular calculation test, run the following command:

   python3 angle_calculator.py --img=images/img1.jpg --bus=7 --ptz

[--img] (default = images/img1.jpg) : the path to your test image
[--bus] (default = 7)		    : the I2C bus used
[--ptz] 	   		    : connect the PTZ camera

if one of these argument is missing, the default value will be used instead